rows.label: qst200812_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh... Going to all this trouble
to heal a tree with no reward...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0002
rows.name:
It seems the Saffronia tree
is very important to you.

rows.label: qst200812_msg0004
rows.name: Do you still have business with Hotaru?

rows.label: qst200812_msg0005
rows.name:
Yeah... I just can't shake the
feeling that the girl is hiding
the classified documents.

rows.label: qst200812_msg0006
rows.name: I told you, I don't have them!

rows.label: qst200812_msg0007
rows.name:
Heh. No one who's trying to
hide something is going to
tell you they have it.

rows.label: qst200812_msg0008
rows.name: So, should I just say I have them?

rows.label: qst200812_msg0010
rows.name: Argh! How can I make you believe me!

rows.label: qst200812_msg0011
rows.name:
So in the end, we have no
choice but to fight...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0013
rows.name:
This time, we've increased
our numbers and have a
carefully planned strategy...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0014
rows.name:
This time, we'll get it
back! Prepare yourselves!
